days_until_so.tooltipText: The Days Until Stockout is the number of Expected Days of Inventory at Amazon based on your current total Expected Domestic Inventory (total FBA Inventory + total 3PL)

expected_inventory.tooltipText: The number of expected inventory level on any given day.

fba_inventory.tooltipText: The number of units you have for an SKU in Amazon fulfillment centers that have been processed: (afn-warehouse-quantity) = (afn-fulfillable-quantity) + (afn-unsellable-quantity) + (afn-reserved-quantity).

Create Order.tooltipText: Smart Order will automatically recommend the next day of order and how many to order, in order to avoid stockouts

Expected Inventory.tooltipText: The number of expected inventory level on any given day
